Candy Land is a classic, simple race-to-the-finish board game for young children, where players move their gingerbread men along a rainbow path to be the first to reach King Kandy's Castle. Players are eliminated from the game by drawing cards with colors, and their gingerbread men advance to the next space of that color. Special cards can lead to shortcuts or send players to certain spaces. It's designed for ages 3 and up and doesn't require reading.
